    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/5",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">In the continuous time framework, there is an implicit nonnegativity constraint on wealth, which is one form of a shortfall constraint (<i>see</i> <b>Merton</b> <b>Problem</b>).</p>",
