      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">binary option, the strategy effectively acts as the delta of the digital option with all the instability of that delta as the term decays if the strike remains unachieved. Strategies that mitigate this fact and therefore minimize the <i>expected shortfall</i> are constructed in [14]. These strategies effectively replicate options with standard put payoffs as opposed to digitals or binaries.</p>",
