      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">and is clearly related to the objectives treated earlier by Browne, Follmer, and Leukert [9, 13, 14] ( ¨ <i>see</i> <b>Value-at-Risk</b>).</p>",
