    {
      "id": "/page/2/Text/6",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">In this framework, the case <i>α</i> = 1 corresponds to the standard benchmark agent that does not limit losses and <i>α</i> = 0 corresponds to the portfolio insurer (or put option purchaser) who maintains his wealth above the floor in all states [3].</p>",
      "page": 449,
      "polygon": [
        [
